      <title>美国要求韩国加强对中国芯片的出口管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/us-asks-south-korea-to-toughen-up-export-controls-on-china-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国要求韩国对向中国出口半导体技术采取类似于华盛顿已经实施的限制，这是拜登政府正在加大力度阻止北京芯片野心的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/us-asks-south-korea-to-toughen-up-export-controls-on-china-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 08:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>极端高温导致菲律宾学校关闭，促使远程授课</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/extreme-heat-shuts-philippine-schools-prompts-remote-classes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温上升促使政府恢复远程学习替代方案，菲律宾周二暂停了全国一些城市的面授课程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/extreme-heat-shuts-philippine-schools-prompts-remote-classes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:57:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡扩大加密货币规则以涵盖托管和更多转账</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/singapore-widens-crypto-rules-to-cover-custody-more-transfers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡扩大了数字资产规则的范围，涵盖代币托管以及更多参与资金转移的公司，这是该城市国家为该行业建立机构中心而做出的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/singapore-widens-crypto-rules-to-cover-custody-more-transfers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者为电动汽车成功的早期迹象欢呼雀跃，小米股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/xiaomi-jumps-as-investors-cheer-early-signs-of-ev-success</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小米公司在香港的股价飙升，因其首款电动汽车的订单超出预期，引发了人们对这家智能手机制造商可能在中国竞争激烈的汽车市场取得成功的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/xiaomi-jumps-as-investors-cheer-early-signs-of-ev-success</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 01:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 接近以 30 亿美元收购合规风险公司 Avetta</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/eqt-said-to-near-3-billion-deal-for-compliance-risk-firm-avetta</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，EQT AB 即将达成收购 Avetta LLC 的交易，这笔交易将使这家合规软件提供商（包括债务）估值约为 30 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/eqt-said-to-near-3-billion-deal-for-compliance-risk-firm-avetta</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本批准向 Chip Venture Rapidus 提供 39 亿美元援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-okays-another-3-9-billion-in-aid-to-chip-venture-rapidus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本批准向芯片企业Rapidus Corp.提供高达5900亿日元（39亿美元）的补贴，为其在半导体制造领域追赶的雄心投入更多资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/japan-okays-another-3-9-billion-in-aid-to-chip-venture-rapidus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡航空将重启飞往中国三个城市的航班：CNA</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/singapore-airlines-to-restart-flights-to-three-china-cities-cna</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡航空有限公司发言人援引新加坡航空发言人的话说，由于“监管原因”暂停了三周的航班，该公司将于本月晚些时候恢复飞往中国三个城市的航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/singapore-airlines-to-restart-flights-to-three-china-cities-cna</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
