      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 21:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乐天发行 12.5 亿美元垃圾债券以重返美国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/rakuten-offers-1-25-billion-junk-bond-in-return-to-us-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐天集团 (Rakuten Group Inc.) 重返高收益债券市场，发行 12.5 亿美元，这是这家负债累累的日本在线零售商试图支撑其财务状况的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/rakuten-offers-1-25-billion-junk-bond-in-return-to-us-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:19:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上最古老的君主制——日本在 Instagram 上首次亮相</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-01/attempting-to-draw-youth-japan-s-royal-family-debuts-instagram-but-so-far-no-candid-photos-shared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京（美联社）——日本皇室周一在 Instagram 上首次亮相，发布了一连串帖子，希望摆脱隐居形象，在社交媒体上接触年轻人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-01/attempting-to-draw-youth-japan-s-royal-family-debuts-instagram-but-so-far-no-candid-photos-shared</guid>
